                                        Tom Bauer<sup>6</sup> <!----></a></span> <span><a aria-label="Visit this author on ORCID website" data-test="orcid-link" target="_blank" href="https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3520-2676"><img src="https://asset.jmir.pub/assets/static/images/Orcid-ID-Logo-Colour.png" alt="Author Orcid Image" aria-label="Author Orcid Image" class="info__orcid-img"></a></span> <!----></span></div> <!----></div></div> <div role="tablist" aria-label="Article" class="tabs"><a href="/2019/4/e15038/" aria-current="page" role="tab" aria-label="Article" data-test="tabs" class="nuxt-link-exact-active nuxt-link-active active">
