49">CrossRef</a>] [<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uids=29300961&amp;dopt=Abstract" target="_blank">Medline</a>]</span></li><li><span id="ref16">Greenwood D, Hankins AI, Parise CA, Spier V, Olveda J, Buss KA. A comparison of in-person, telephone, and secure messaging for type 2 diabetes self-management support. Diabetes Educ  2014 Jul;40(4):516-525. [<a target="_blank" href="https://dx.doi.org/10.1177/0145721714531337">CrossRef</a>] [<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uids=24742540&amp;dopt=Abstract" target="_blank">Medline</a>]</span></li><li><span id="ref17">Jhamb M, Cavanaugh KL, Bian A, Chen G, Ikizler TA, Unruh ML,  et al. Disparities in electronic health record patient portal use in nephrology clinics. Clin J Am Soc Nephrol  2015 Nov 6;10(11):2013-2022  [<a href="http://cjasn.asnjournals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&amp;pmid=26493242" target="_blank">FREE Full text</a>] [<a target="_blank" href="https://dx.doi.org/10.2215/CJN.01640215">CrossRef</a>] [<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uids=26493242&amp;dopt=Abstract" target="_blank">Medline</a>]</span></li><li><span id="ref18">Lee J, Kim JG, Jin M, Ahn K, Kim B, Kim S,  et al. Beneficial effects of two types of personal health record services connected with electronic medical records within the hospital setting. Comput Inform Nurs  2017 Nov;35(11):574-581. [<a target="_blank" href="https://dx.doi.org/10.1097/CIN.0000000000000362">CrossRef</a>] [<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=PubMed&amp;list_uids=28548973&amp;dopt=Abstract" target="_blank">Medline</a>]</span></li><li><span id="ref19">Milani RV, Lavie CJ, Bober RM, Milani AR, Ventura HO. Improving hypertension control and patient engagement using digital tools. Am J Med  2017 Jan;130(1):14-20. [<a target="_blank" href="https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j